title: FRAM Extra Guard PH4967, 10K Mile Change Interval Spin-On Oil Filter, black
description: FRAM Extra Guard Oil Filters feature proven protection for up to 5,000 miles and are engineered for use with conventional oil. With an ideal balance of dirt-trapping efficiency and dirt-holding capacity, FRAM Extra Guard oil filters use a special blend of fibers and resin to create a proprietary filter media that delivers excellent engine protection. Extra Guard is the perfect filter for everyday drivers who perform frequent maintenance on their vehicles.
